parallel

Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • parallel.Manager

  • public class Manager
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Pete Meltzer on 05/08/17.

    Main control logic for preProcessing and launching threads.

    All shared data for the Producers and Consumers is stored here.
